Feel free to use or modify.

This script will extract an archive of the following types into the current
directory: tar.bz2 (and tbz2), tar.gz (and tgz), 7-zip, zip (and jar), 
bzip2 (and gzip), xz and rar.

It depends on gzip, bzip2, unrar, unzip, 7z, xz and tar being available in the
path to do this.
